cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.NE 

This paper discusses the use of machine learning techniques for the automatic extraction of causal relationships from natural language texts. Therefore, it is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-categories of Computational Linguistics (cs.CL), Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI), and Machine Learning (cs.LG). Additionally, the paper discusses the use of labelled data and the analysis of strengths and weaknesses of different techniques, which suggests that it may also belong to the Information Retrieval (cs.IR) and Neural and Evolutionary Computing (cs.NE) sub-categories.
